Achievements.Name: Too Much Free Time
Achievements.Description: Patience. Hours and hours of patience.

Achievements.Name: To Points Unknown
Achievements.Description: The journey of 100,000 km begins with a single step.

Achievements.Name: Grand Battles
Achievements.Description: Monsters! Bring on the monsters!

Achievements.Name: Jackpot
Achievements.Description: Win more chips!

Achievements.Name: Piggybank
Achievements.Description: Save more Gald. More. No, seriously. A lot more.

Achievements.Name: They Call Me...
Achievements.Description: Clear sub events to acquire titles.

Achievements.Name: Character Study
Achievements.Description: Careful! Some skits are only available for a limited time.

Achievements.Name: No More Grinding
Achievements.Description: Just fight and fight until you don't really need to fight anymore.

Achievements.Name: Map Nerd
Achievements.Description: The camera reveals what the World Map holds...

Achievements.Name: Monster Nerd
Achievements.Description: Don't forget to use a Magic Lens or two. Or more.

Achievements.Name: Item Nerd
Achievements.Description: Careful! Some items are only available through synthesis.

Achievements.Name: Little Mad Scientist
Achievements.Description: Synthesize! Mash stuff up! Make lots of things!

Achievements.Name: Back Up Plan
Achievements.Description: Save points are located all over the world.

Achievements.Name: Vesperia Master
Achievements.Description: Aim for total completion.

Achievements.Name: The Hit that Keeps On Hitting
Achievements.Description: Keep that combo going and going and going!

Achievements.Name: Eureka!
Achievements.Description: You used Synthesis to create new equipment and items. Keep it up!

Achievements.Name: First Strike
Achievements.Description: Took out your enemy in a single shot! Master this technique to gain advantage in battles.

Achievements.Name: Big Game Greenhorn
Achievements.Description: Giganto Monsters are...special. Big. Strong. Nasty. Have fun!

Achievements.Name: Big Game Hunter
Achievements.Description: You slew all Giganto Monsters! Nothing can stand before you! Careful, though. It's a big world...

Achievements.Name: Smarty-pants
Achievements.Description: Hey! You answered every quiz question right! You are a true Tales fan. Thank you.

Achievements.Name: Speedster
Achievements.Description: Whoa! Easy! Could you be any faster?! Relax. Take your time. There's much more to discover...

Achievements.Name: Ahhh, Memories
Achievements.Description: You have cleared the Labyrinth of Memories. Did you enjoy the surprise?

Achievements.Name: Recovered the Aque Blastia
Achievements.Description: You took back the aque blastia core from Barbos. This should fix the lower quarter's fountain.

Achievements.Name: Ended Alexei's Ambitions
Achievements.Description: You put an end to Alexei's ambitions. However, the Adephagos remains. The battle continues...

Achievements.Name: Defeated the Adephagos
Achievements.Description: You defeated the Adephagos with Duke! A new world begins. A world without blastia.

Achievements.Name: Bunny Guild Member
Achievements.Description: Somehow, somewhere, you became an official member of the Bunny Guild. Who needs Brave Vesperia?

Achievements.Name: Low Level Challenger
Achievements.Description: You defeated Barbos at Lv. 15 or under! Amazing! You sure know how to take this guy down.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 1
Achievements.Description: Defeated Zagi while protecting Estellise from Zagi's attacks.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 2
Achievements.Description: Downed Goliath by attacking its Achilles' heel while it charged X Buster.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 3
Achievements.Description: Learning from Karol's experience, you used the billybally plants to stun Gattuso.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 4
Achievements.Description: Lured Zagi to the side of the ship and knocked him overboard to cool him off!

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 5
Achievements.Description: Downed the Dreaded Giant when it reared back and left itself wide open.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 6
Achievements.Description: Raven used Serpent to set a trap for the Gigalarva and prevented it from healing itself.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 7
Achievements.Description: VS Barbos. You took out the bridge supports, keeping him from calling out more of his thugs.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 8
Achievements.Description: Third battle VS. Zagi. Let him absorb too much magic, destroying his bohdi blastia.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 9
Achievements.Description: VS. Pteropus. You defeated the Leader Bat and prevented Pteropus from recombining.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 10
Achievements.Description: VS. Outbreaker. You destroyed the core and prevented magic from inverting day and night.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 11
Achievements.Description: VS. Belius. You lit up all candlesticks and eliminated the illusions.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 12
Achievements.Description: VS. Nan and Tison. Timed your strikes between their attacks and knocked them down.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 13
Achievements.Description: VS. Schwann. Downed him by attacking when he was clutching his heart after his mystic arte.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 14
Achievements.Description: Fourth battle VS. Zagi. Used Karol's Nice Recovery Smash arte to force him to recover from poison.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 15
Achievements.Description: VS. Baitojoh. Hit it 3 times during it's Ice Edge attack and fished it out of the water.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 16
Achievements.Description: VS. Estellise. Used the item, Mother's Memento.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 17
Achievements.Description: VS. Yeager. Made his heart explode using Raven's Rain arte.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 18
Achievements.Description: VS. Alexei. Downed him by attacking when he was tired after his mystic arte.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 19
Achievements.Description: VS. Gusios. Attacked his tail, then downed him with a close attack while his feet were raised.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 20
Achievements.Description: VS. Khroma. Downed her by timing your strikes between certain of her attacks.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 21
Achievements.Description: VS. Flynn. He used every arte he could, including a mystic arte.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 22
Achievements.Description: Fifth battle VS. Zagi. Downed him by attacking after he becomes exhausted from Blastia Bane.

Achievements.Name: Secret Mission 23
Achievements.Description: Defeated Duke using a mystic arte.
